Package: imf.data
Title: An Interface to IMF (International Monetary Fund) Data
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("Pedro", "Baltazar",, "pedrobtz@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: Provides low-level access to the International Monetary Fund
    Statistical Data and Metadata eXchange ('SDMX') 3.0 API and a concise
    workflow for discovering datasets, inspecting dimensions, and
    downloading observations as tidy data frames.
